# Construction toolkit is private EXCEPT the read-only utilities below, which CI and
# the weekly source monitor run on GitHub. The corpus stays independently verifiable
# regardless: originals + text + hashes + open schemas are all published.
scripts/*
!scripts/hashing.py
!scripts/validate_corpus.py
!scripts/watch_sources.py
!scripts/audit_sources.py
# The reproducibility POLICY is public (what is declared excluded, and the backlog ceiling) —
# transparency of the corpus's own claims. The GATE that reads it (repro_gate.py) and the
# extraction engine (extract.py) stay private, provided from the toolkit at build time.
!scripts/repro-policy.json
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.DS_Store
_capture/
# Internal design-lock kept private; not part of the public corpus.
docs/design-lock.md
